---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | Fruit Joy - Cute Fruit Match Game" 
  description="Learn more about Fruit Joy, the cutest fruit merge puzzle game online. Made for kids and players of all ages!"
>
  <Navbar />

  <main class="w-full bg-canvas py-16 transition-colors duration-200">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      
      <!-- Path breadcrumb/header -->
      <div class="mb-10 text-left border-b-3 border-[#2c1e13]/10 pb-8 font-black text-[#2c1e13]">
        <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 border-2 border-[#2c1e13] text-[10px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">About Us</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mt-3 mb-2">
          About Fruit Joy 🍒
        </h1>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          The story of a cute, physics-based matching game built for everyone to enjoy!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Article content styled with playful guidelines -->
      <article class="text-stone-600 dark:text-body leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-6 select-text font-bold">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#2c1e13] dark:text-ink mb-3">Our Mission 🌟</h2>
          <p>
            At <strong>Fruit Joy</strong>, we believe that web games should be super fast, adorable, and completely free of annoying ads. We took the highly engaging, physics-based fruit matching formula (popularized by Suika Game) and redesigned it with a colorful, playful cartoon theme. Every single fruit has a cute happy face and glowing cheeks to make your gameplay experience as cheerful as possible!
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="border-t-2 border-[#2c1e13]/10 pt-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#2c1e13] dark:text-ink mb-3">The Technology Stack 🛠️</h2>
          <p>
            Fruit Joy uses advanced web technologies behind the scenes to keep the game running at a silky-smooth 60 frames per second:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-2 text-xs font-black">
            <li>
              <strong>Astro (v6)</strong>: Powers our fast, search-friendly website.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Matter.js</strong>: Handles the realistic bouncing and rolling of our cute round fruits.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Tailwind CSS (v4)</strong>: Styles our pages with bright, playful, and responsive layouts.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Web Audio API</strong>: Generates cute pop and merge sounds on-the-fly!
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="border-t-2 border-[#2c1e13]/10 pt-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#2c1e13] dark:text-ink mb-3">Matching Fun & Joy! 🎉</h2>
          <p>
            In Fruit Joy, every fruit can merge into a bigger one when it touches a matching fruit. 
            Keep matching to clear up space, and aim carefully so they don't pile up into the danger zone at the top!
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="border-3 border-[#2c1e13] bg-amber-50 dark:bg-canvas-soft-2 p-6 rounded-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-black text-[#2c1e13] dark:text-ink mb-2">No Ads, Safe for Everyone 🔒</h2>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">
            We are dedicated to maintaining a clean and safe website. That means no tracking, no cookies, and no video ads. Just pure, clean matching fun for the whole family! Thank you for playing and sharing Fruit Joy!
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
